'''Rae''' was a [[Gender/Legends|female]] green-skinned [[Alien/Legends|alien]] racketeer who had an aunt named [[Bles]], and a sibling named [[Dran]]. Their culture emphasized family commitment over mere technicalities such as legal niceties. They took little part in the social whirl, though in fights Rae and Dran would obey orders given by Bles. They were aboard the ship ''[[Ananuru Express]]'' when the secret [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[RNA brainwashing virus]] [[Data-tape/Legends|datatape]] was up for auction. Before the auction could begin, however, Bles ordered her family to search the suites to see if they could steal it.

